metadata.name: Canary #1
metadata.description: The elusive bird of hope and joy, fleeting and impossible to obtain if one doesnâ€™t hold faith in its existence. A conceptual piece with the most rudimental design in the entire collection, a metaphor for the simple dream we are all wishing for. Legend says that being in possession of the bluebird will help one find true love, happiness and peace, and make their wildest dreams come true. Provides exclusive membership in MIHAVERSE.
metadata.provenance: Due to minor changes to the artworks prior mint, token order was re-randomized and provenance had to be re-generated offchain and provided to the community on our Discord server.
